data.description: One of a kind townhome just over a mile from the Beautiful Marietta Square.  3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths located just a few doors from the Cul-De-Sac.  The only home in the neighborhood featuring a home office on the main level plus a sitting room/private exercise area in the spacious Master Suite.  Enjoy your private and fenced back yard or go for a swim in the community pool just a short stroll around the corner.  Hardwood Floors throughout upstairs and the main level. No carpet.  Private closed circuit cameras at front and back entrances, and the garage will stay with this lovely home.  Dine out tonight with so many convenient options nearby at the Marietta Square.  Easy commute to nearby shopping such as Town Center Mall, or the Avenues at West Cobb or if You must, take a easy drive to I-75 and go to work. New garage doors added 2021. Additional built in cabinet, new updated light fixtures, smart home.
